query:
INSERT INTO profile (
            user_id,
            zoom_url,
            avatar_url,
            telegram_id
        )
        VALUES (
            $1,
            $2,
            $3,
            $4
        )
        ON CONFLICT (user_id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            zoom_url = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.zoom_url, profile.zoom_url),
            avatar_url = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.avatar_url, profile.avatar_url),
            telegram_id = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.telegram_id, profile.telegram_id)
        RETURNING *
